    "description": "S.R. Batliboi Advisory Limited is actively seeking a talented and motivated Credit Analyst to join our dynamic team in Amritsar. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout S.R. Batliboi Advisory Limited:\nS.R. Batliboi Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Monitor financial performance against targets and provide variance analysis\n• Conduct due diligence for mergers, acquisitions, and investments\n• Liaise with banks, regulators, and financial institutions\n• Implement and maintain internal controls and audit procedures\n• Manage credit risk assessment and loan appraisal processes\n• Prepare MIS reports for senior management review\n• Prepare and analyze financial statements, reports, and budgets\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Tech / B.E. in Computer Science or related discipline\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Python for Finance\n• Proficiency in GST\n• Proficiency in Credit Analysis\n• Proficiency in Financial Reporting\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Tally\n• Proficiency in Income Tax\n• Proficiency in QuickBooks\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Amritsar, Punjab, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with S.R. Batliboi Advisory Limited!",
